03:23.324 --> 03:40.091
me at many professional meetings that it was just a 
matter of time until he would recruit me back to

03:23.324 --> 03:40.091
Texas A&M for faculty. So after I'd been at Cornell 
five years, Dr. Bloodworth came along with a

